{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Play Hide and Seek online with your friends!</h2><br>Hide and Seek is a first person multiplayer &quot;FPS&quot; game where you play hide and seek in various environments. Hide and Seek follows the traditional 1 Seeker vs many Hiders model of hide and seek that everyone is familiar with.<br>Hide and Seek was developed by a single developer! It took more than 2 years for the first release, and still is being developed.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2>As a <strong>Hider</strong> you have a short period of time to get away from <strong>Base</strong> after the round starts. The <strong>Seeker</strong> will be stuck in <strong>Base</strong> until that time expires. <strong>Base</strong> will then be locked for a period of time. During this time, all <strong>Hiders</strong> must try to stay away from the <strong>Seeker</strong>, who will be hunting for them. Once this <i>Hide Time</i> expires, <strong>Base</strong> will reopen and all <strong>Hiders</strong> must make it back before the round ends.<br><br>Hide and Seek requires an internet connection to play. You can host your server own through the in-game menus, or join one someone else is hosting. Don't see a server you like? Join up with some friends and host a LAN party.<br><br>Hide and Seek is 100% free to play. There are no costs to play or to host your own server.<br><br>If you wish to support the continued development of Hide and Seek consider purchasing a Hat or two.<br><br>Visit the Steam Community Hub to leave suggestions or feedback, find groups to play with, and stay up to date with all news.","achievements":{"total":0},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/596940/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1515707243","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/596940/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1515707243","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/596940/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1515707243","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/596940/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1515707243","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Play Hide and Seek online with your friends!</h2><br>Hide and Seek is a first person multiplayer &quot;FPS&quot; game where you play hide and seek in various environments. Hide and Seek follows the traditional 1 Seeker vs many Hiders model of hide and seek that everyone is familiar with.<br>Hide and Seek was developed by a single developer! It took more than 2 years for the first release, and still is being developed.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2>As a <strong>Hider</strong> you have a short period of time to get away from <strong>Base</strong> after the round starts. The <strong>Seeker</strong> will be stuck in <strong>Base</strong> until that time expires. <strong>Base</strong> will then be locked for a period of time. During this time, all <strong>Hiders</strong> must try to stay away from the <strong>Seeker</strong>, who will be hunting for them. Once this <i>Hide Time</i> expires, <strong>Base</strong> will reopen and all <strong>Hiders</strong> must make it back before the round ends.<br><br>Hide and Seek requires an internet connection to play. You can host your server own through the in-game menus, or join one someone else is hosting. Don't see a server you like? Join up with some friends and host a LAN party.<br><br>Hide and Seek is 100% free to play. There are no costs to play or to host your own server.<br><br>If you wish to support the continued development of Hide and Seek consider purchasing a Hat or two.<br><br>Visit the Steam Community Hub to leave suggestions or feedback, find groups to play with, and stay up to date with all news.","developers":["Llama Software"],"dlc":[689430,693590,693600,693601,693602,693603,693604,693605,693606,693607,693608,693609,693610,693611,693612,693613,693614,693615,693616,693617,693618,693619,693620,693621,693622,693623,693624,693625,693626,693627,693628,693629,693630,693631,693632,693633,693634,693635,693636,693637,693638,693639,693641,693642,693643,693644],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Free To Play","id":"37"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/596940/header.jpg?t=1515707243","is_free":true,"legal_notice":"Copyright Llama Software 2017","linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256705631,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256705631/movie480.mp4?t=1515707214","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256705631/movie_max.mp4?t=1515707214"},"name":"Haunted House Map Overview (1.0.3.53)","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256705631/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1515707214","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256705631/movie480.webm?t=1515707214","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256705631/movie_max.webm?t=1515707214"}},{"highlight":true,"id":256684739,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256684739/movie480.mp4?t=1515707224","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256684739/movie_max.mp4?t=1515707224"},"name":"Hide and Seek Hedge Maze Preview (pre-1.0.3.53)","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256684739/movie.29